{"serial": "13006", "department_serial": 12, "code": "FR1034", "class": "A", "name": {"en": "Grammar and Composition", "ch": "文法與寫作"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Hsu, Chia-Hua"], "ch": ["徐佳華"]}, "credits": 4, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "103"}}, {"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "103"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": true, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "法國語文學系", "en": "Department of French"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 26, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "介紹基本文法及其應用，使初學者掌握法語最基本的規範，得以造出簡單、正確的句子。", "en": "Please refer to the Chinese version."}, "outline": {"ch": "1) 文法部份：介紹基本文法及其應用，使初學者掌握法語最基本的規範，得以造出簡單、正確的句子。選用 Nouvelle Grammaire du francais (ed.　Hachette) 為教材，配合自編講義，照授課大綱所列之各單元循序漸進，講解法文文法基本原則，並輔以例句，再做練習題分析比較。\n上學期單元為: le pronom sujet / les verbes　etre et avoir, les constructions il y a, c’est, ce sont / le nom et l’article / l’interrogation et la negation / l’adjectif (I) – masculin et feminin, singulier et pluriel / les verbes en er au present, les verbes suivis d’une preposition / l’adjectif (II) – l’accord de l’adj. / les verbes en ir au present / les possessifs – adjectif et pronom / les verbes irreguliers au present (I) / les demonstratifs – adjectif et pronom / l’adjectif (III) – la place de l’adjectif / les adverbes / les verbes irreguliers au present (II) / Quelques constructions verbales et les auxiliaires / le futur / le participe passe et le passe compose / les indefinis / le comparatif et le superlatif\n下學期單元為: l’imperatif / les verbes pronominaux / les pronoms complements / les pronoms y et en / l’ordre des pronoms complements / l’imperatif et les pronoms / l’imparfait / le plus-que-parfait / le futur anterieur / la voix passive / le pronom relatif / le participe et le gerondif / le conditionnel\n2) 寫作部份：讓學生運用所學之文法觀念與規則，透過翻譯、造句、短文寫作練習、字彙運用練習達到寫作基本簡單句及複雜句之能力，並為二年級之 ? 寫作二 ?及 ? 翻譯 一?奠定基礎。\n作業除個別批改外，並將全班同學共同常犯的典型錯誤、句型打字成講義，上課共同思考、訂正。", "en": "Please refer to the Chinese version."}, "textbook": {"ch": "* Nouvelle Grammaire du francais, Hachette. \n* Nouvelle Grammaire du francais (cours de civilisation francaise de la Sorbonne), edition Hachette.\n* 350 exercices (niveau debutant), Hachette.\n* Claire Leroy-Miquel et Anne Goliot-Lete, Vocabulaire progressif du francais, CLE international.\n* Grammaire progressive du Francais, Cle international.\n* Le Premier Livre de francais, methode Marchand, F.E.L.F. \n* 岳家君，《法語語法詳解》，敦煌書局。\n* 法語簡易文法與練習 Premiers pas en grammaire du francais, 中央圖書出版社。", "en": "Please refer to the Chinese version."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "平時成績：40％（含作業及小考）/ 期中考：30％ / 期末考：30％", "en": "Please refer to the Chinese version."}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週一第二、八節、週四第二、五節", "en": "Lundi 9h-10h et 16h-17h ; jeudi 9h-10h et 13h à 14h"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "實體課程搭配數位影音課程及教材", "en": "Mixed-mode instruction. Physical classes with additional online materials."}, "domain": {"ch": "語言訓練", "en": "語言訓練"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "自學能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "多元文化觀", "rating": "(1)非常低", "assesments": ["無"]}, {"competencies": "審美欣賞", "rating": "(1)非常低", "assesments": ["無"]}, {"competencies": "創意思考", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯批判", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Competence in linguistic expression", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Autodi